OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater bills to rise above  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finflation in April         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Water companies are forecasting an     
OL,6, above-inflation rise in average        
OL,7, household bills in April, drawing      
OL,8, criticism from campaigners.            
OL,10,FThe average annual water and sewerage  
OL,11,Fbill is expected to rise by 6% in      
OL,12,FEngland and Wales, up #27 to #473, says
OL,13,Fsuppliers' trade body Water UK.        
OL,15,FIn Scotland, water and waste charges   
OL,16,Fwill go up by 8.8%, a rise of #36.     
OL,18,FWater firms have been facing intense   
OL,19,Fscrutiny after the dumping of sewage   
OL,20,Finto rivers.                           
